                <note rend="inline" type="source">812.00/15629½a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to President
                            <persName type="to">Wilson</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-07-31T11:53:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 31, 1915—11:53 a. m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Six Latin American diplomats have agreed to be here Thursday, August 5th for
                    informal conference. When do you think it would be well to make public
                    announcement that conference is to take place. <pb facs="0588" n="542"
                        xml:id="pg_542"/> Believe that announcement will have beneficial effect in
                    Mexico and in this country, as indicating intention to proceed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Robert Lansing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
